- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is relevant as the paper uses generative adversarial networks (GAN) for image refinement. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is relevant as the paper deals with training an object detector using synthetic data. 
- cs.GR (Graphics) is relevant as the paper uses domain randomization procedures to generate synthetic images.
